  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      comparison between different methods in fixation of comminuted distal radius fractures&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This clinical study aims at comparison of treatment outcomes of Spanning plate versus&#xD;
      spanning External fixator in fixation of comminuted distal radius fracture.&#xD;
&#xD;
      The primary outcomes that we like to measure are pain, healing. Stiffness and range of motion&#xD;
      .&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
